13)addition  and sub of two matrix:
m<-matrix(c(1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9),3,3)
n<-matrix(c(1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9),3,3)
print("Addition of two matrix::")
print(m+n)
print("Substacrion of two matrix::")
print(m-n)

